{"tid":48001,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過抽後算賬拎第二張黃牌？","createTime":"2016-12-20T18:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T18:42:23.000Z","uid":22538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef418f35c58157aea67ff0374d79e292fbc01f0","tid":48001,"uid":22538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:05:02.000Z","msg":"或者本身球員A(冇牌)犯規<br />\n球証俾得益對面諗著出界先抽後算賬<br />\n點知未俾牌 個球員A又犯多次<br />\n是咪一野比兩張黃牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fc65aae727fc1d6d869c707bf873670776b67e","tid":48001,"uid":48858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:08:28.000Z","msg":"秋後比第2張黃牌應該就無啦，要比就應該即時比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於一野比2張黃，印象中係有試過"},{"pid":"f505f9ce59d4c544c1e26a9e0d2d9119f705063c","tid":48001,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:10:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90db51d047f862ed4c7a4f6f964e94c76a5ac359","tid":48001,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:11:52.000Z","msg":"通常都係抽完先俾牌嘅<br />\n俾第幾張就視乎佢之前有無拎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e6e0a52e97db8f7274dc6bdb58b8ad89d1fc2b","tid":48001,"uid":22538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:12:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>秋後比第2張黃牌應該就無啦，要比就應該即時比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於一野比2張黃，印象中係有試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 我印象中都係如果要俾第二張黃會立即俾<br />\n但一野2張黃好似冇印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6bf346b9feeeb885e629dba1b2c8bf5449a203","tid":48001,"uid":22538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常都係抽完先俾牌嘅<br />\n俾第幾張就視乎佢之前有無拎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係佢0黃先可以抽後？<br />\n本身有1黃再黃就要立即俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9654eb74d9ca2e424a45440720c56867f78e4f1a","tid":48001,"uid":15199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>秋後比第2張黃牌應該就無啦，要比就應該即時比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於一野比2張黃，印象中係有試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 我印象中都係如果要俾第二張黃會立即俾<br />\n但一野2張黃好似冇印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食完牌嘈/屌球證"},{"pid":"f97cbdf5823c9a99bcbc40869ac15eae644f67d7","tid":48001,"uid":22538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>秋後比第2張黃牌應該就無啦，要比就應該即時比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於一野比2張黃，印象中係有試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 我印象中都係如果要俾第二張黃會立即俾<br />\n但一野2張黃好似冇印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食完牌嘈/屌球證</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又係啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4e22febdbe872831f0264c7a680a1856bdd08b","tid":48001,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:20:44.000Z","msg":"屌球証 不服判決 連食兩黃<br />\n比得益都可以後補黃牌 算唔算抽後？"},{"pid":"0dbd2b360d37937efc4e14ee0a83145bf327a276","tid":48001,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:22:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌球証 不服判決 連食兩黃<br />\n比得益都可以後補黃牌 算唔算抽後？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來就係講得益<br />\n未見過連黃"},{"pid":"8d81e9ad98ee37795571ccdd3d4aff761be45d56","tid":48001,"uid":22538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌球証 不服判決 連食兩黃<br />\n比得益都可以後補黃牌 算唔算抽後？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry 我解釋得唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抽後算脹就係